OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FArgyll mostly cloudy with
OL,6,Foccasional showers. Drier with
OL,7,Fbrighter spells from the Central Belt
OL,8,Fsouthwards in the morning. Showers
OL,9,Fbuilding across the area later in the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Winds freshening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLargely cloudy throughout the
OL,13,Fevening and overnight with showers,
OL,14,Fthese heavy at times and occasionally
OL,15,Fforming longer spells of rain. Best
OL,16,Fchance of drier, clearer spells in the
OL,17,Fsouth. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
