OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloudy for Argyll with
OL,6,Fscattered showers or occasionally
OL,7,Flonger spells of rain. Best of drier
OL,8,Fand brighter spells in the south and
OL,9,Feast.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry and
OL,12,Fbecoming increasingly sunny on Sunday.
OL,13,FDry and bright start on Monday, rain
OL,14,Ffrom southwest later. Mostly cloudy
OL,15,FTuesday with rain or showers. Becoming
OL,16,Fwarmer.
